        <details><summary>Where do you pick us up?</summary><div>Hotels, lounges, and venues across Las Vegas, Henderson, Summerlin, and North Las Vegas. Off-Strip pickups and Airbnb pickups are fully accommodated.</div></details>
        <details><summary>Can we split payment across our group?</summary><div>Yes — payment can be split up to 3 ways. For large corporate groups requiring invoicing, contact us directly at info@gxptours.com.</div></details>
